{
  "video_id": "L375-rWJVmU",
  "title": "My journey to thank all the people responsible for my morning coffee | A.J. Jacobs",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15680.0,
      "text": "So, I don&#39;t like to boast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15719.0,
      "end_time": 21256.0,
      "text": "but I am very good at finding things to be annoyed about."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21280.0,
      "end_time": 23376.0,
      "text": "It is a real specialty of mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23400.0,
      "end_time": 27296.0,
      "text": "I can hear 100 compliments and a single insult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27320.0,
      "end_time": 28816.0,
      "text": "and what do I remember?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28840.0,
      "end_time": 30216.0,
      "text": "The insult."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30240.0,
      "end_time": 32936.0,
      "text": "And according to the research, I&#39;m not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32960.0,
      "end_time": 38496.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the human brain is wired to focus on the negative."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38520.0,
      "end_time": 41856.0,
      "text": "Now, this might have been helpful when we were cave people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41880.0,
      "end_time": 43736.0,
      "text": "trying to avoid predators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43760.0,
      "end_time": 46455.0,
      "text": "but now it&#39;s a terrible way to go through life."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46480.0,
      "end_time": 52936.0,
      "text": "It is a real major component of anxiety and depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52960.0,
      "end_time": 57160.0,
      "text": "So how can we fight the brain&#39;s negative bias?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57400.0,
      "end_time": 62360.0,
      "text": "According to a lot of research, one of the best weapons is gratitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63800.0,
      "end_time": 68960.0,
      "text": "So knowing this, I started a new tradition in our house a couple of years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 68120.0,
      "end_time": 70576.0,
      "text": "Before a meal with my wife and kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70600.0,
      "end_time": 73440.0,
      "text": "I would say a prayer of thanksgiving."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 74560.0,
      "end_time": 76376.0,
      "text": "Prayer is not quite the right word."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76400.0,
      "end_time": 81960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m agnostic, so instead of thanking God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81120.0,
      "end_time": 85456.0,
      "text": "I would thank some of the people who helped make my food a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85480.0,
      "end_time": 89816.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d say, \"I&#39;d like to thank the farmer who grew these tomatoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89840.0,
      "end_time": 92536.0,
      "text": "and the trucker who drove these tomatoes to the store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92560.0,
      "end_time": 95416.0,
      "text": "and the cashier who rang these tomatoes up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95440.0,
      "end_time": 98390.0,
      "text": "And I thought it was going pretty well, this tradition."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99400.0,
      "end_time": 101576.0,
      "text": "Then one day, my 10-year-old son said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 101600.0,
      "end_time": 104936.0,
      "text": "\"You know, Dad, those people aren&#39;t in our apartment."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104960.0,
      "end_time": 106175.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t hear you."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106200.0,
      "end_time": 110256.0,
      "text": "If you really cared, you would go and thank them in person.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 110280.0,
      "end_time": 113456.0,
      "text": "And I thought, \"Hmm. That&#39;s an interesting idea.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113480.0,
      "end_time": 114776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114800.0,
      "end_time": 119856.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m a writer, and for my books I like to go on adventures."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119880.0,
      "end_time": 121295.0,
      "text": "Go on quests."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 121320.0,
      "end_time": 125375.0,
      "text": "So I decided I&#39;m going to take my son up on his challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125400.0,
      "end_time": 127960.0,
      "text": "It seemed simple enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127120.0,
      "end_time": 128976.0,
      "text": "And to make it even simpler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129000.0,
      "end_time": 132496.0,
      "text": "I decided to focus on just one item."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132520.0,
      "end_time": 134336.0,
      "text": "An item I can&#39;t live without:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134360.0,
      "end_time": 136000.0,
      "text": "my morning cup of coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136840.0,
      "end_time": 140560.0,
      "text": "Well, it turned out to be not so simple at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140800.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141120.0,
      "end_time": 142735.0,
      "text": "This quest took me months."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142759.0,
      "end_time": 145215.0,
      "text": "It took me around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145240.0,
      "end_time": 150696.0,
      "text": "Because I discovered that my coffee would not be possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150720.0,
      "end_time": 153776.0,
      "text": "without hundreds of people I take for granted."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153800.0,
      "end_time": 155696.0,
      "text": "So I would thank the trucker"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155720.0,
      "end_time": 158416.0,
      "text": "who drove the coffee beans to the coffee shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158440.0,
      "end_time": 161736.0,
      "text": "But he couldn&#39;t have done his job without the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161760.0,
      "end_time": 164655.0,
      "text": "So I would thank the people who paved the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164680.0,
      "end_time": 165776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165800.0,
      "end_time": 170816.0,
      "text": "And then I would thank the people who made the asphalt for the pavement."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170840.0,
      "end_time": 174896.0,
      "text": "And I came to realize that my coffee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174920.0,
      "end_time": 176976.0,
      "text": "like so much else in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177000.0,
      "end_time": 179496.0,
      "text": "requires the combined work"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179520.0,
      "end_time": 183960.0,
      "text": "of a shocking number of people from all walks of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183120.0,
      "end_time": 188896.0,
      "text": "Architects, biologists, designers, miners, goat herds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 188920.0,
      "end_time": 190416.0,
      "text": "you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190440.0,
      "end_time": 192696.0,
      "text": "I decided to call my project"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192720.0,
      "end_time": 194696.0,
      "text": "\"Thanks a Thousand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194720.0,
      "end_time": 197480.0,
      "text": "Because I ended up thanking over a thousand people."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198400.0,
      "end_time": 201976.0,
      "text": "And it was overwhelming, but it was also wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202000.0,
      "end_time": 204256.0,
      "text": "Because it allowed me to focus"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204280.0,
      "end_time": 207616.0,
      "text": "on the hundreds of things that go right every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 210375.0,
      "text": "as opposed to the three or four that go wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 210400.0,
      "end_time": 216616.0,
      "text": "And it reminded me of the astounding interconnectedness or our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216640.0,
      "end_time": 220495.0,
      "text": "I learned dozens of lessons during this project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220520.0,
      "end_time": 223416.0,
      "text": "but let me just focus on five today."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223440.0,
      "end_time": 226335.0,
      "text": "The first is: look up."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 226360.0,
      "end_time": 228376.0,
      "text": "I started my trail of gratitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 228400.0,
      "end_time": 231696.0,
      "text": "by thanking the barista at my local coffee shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 231720.0,
      "end_time": 233376.0,
      "text": "Joe Coffee in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 233400.0,
      "end_time": 235960.0,
      "text": "Her name is Chung,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 239856.0,
      "text": "and Chung is one of the most upbeat people you will ever meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239880.0,
      "end_time": 243216.0,
      "text": "Big smiler, enthusiastic hugger."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243240.0,
      "end_time": 246736.0,
      "text": "But even for Chung, being a barista is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246760.0,
      "end_time": 251655.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because you are encountering people in a very dangerous state."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251680.0,
      "end_time": 252936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 252960.0,
      "end_time": 255696.0,
      "text": "You know what it is -- precaffeination."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255720.0,
      "end_time": 257856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257880.0,
      "end_time": 261616.0,
      "text": "So, Chung has had people yell at her until she cried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 261640.0,
      "end_time": 263656.0,
      "text": "including a nine-year-old girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263680.0,
      "end_time": 267936.0,
      "text": "who didn&#39;t like the whipped cream design that Chung did on her hot chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267960.0,
      "end_time": 270856.0,
      "text": "So I thanked Chung,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270880.0,
      "end_time": 274550.0,
      "text": "and she thanked me for thanking her."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 274790.0,
      "end_time": 275336.0,
      "text": "I cut it off there."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 275360.0,
      "end_time": 277776.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t want to go into an infinite thanking loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 277800.0,
      "end_time": 279376.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279400.0,
      "end_time": 283135.0,
      "text": "But Chung said that the hardest part"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 286656.0,
      "text": "is when people don&#39;t even treat her like a human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286680.0,
      "end_time": 288536.0,
      "text": "They treat her like a vending machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 288560.0,
      "end_time": 291560.0,
      "text": "So, they&#39;ll hand her their credit card"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291800.0,
      "end_time": 293895.0,
      "text": "without even looking up from their phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 293920.0,
      "end_time": 298736.0,
      "text": "And while she&#39;s saying this, I&#39;m realizing I&#39;ve done that."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 298760.0,
      "end_time": 300616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been that a-hole."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 300640.0,
      "end_time": 303575.0,
      "text": "And at that moment, I pledged:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 303600.0,
      "end_time": 306896.0,
      "text": "when dealing with people, I&#39;m going to take those two seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 306920.0,
      "end_time": 309776.0,
      "text": "and look at them, make eye contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 312656.0,
      "text": "Because it reminds you, you&#39;re dealing with a human being"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312680.0,
      "end_time": 316416.0,
      "text": "who has family and aspirations"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316440.0,
      "end_time": 319160.0,
      "text": "and embarrassing high school memories."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319400.0,
      "end_time": 322960.0,
      "text": "And that little moment of connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322120.0,
      "end_time": 326816.0,
      "text": "is so important to both people&#39;s humanity and happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 326840.0,
      "end_time": 328616.0,
      "text": "Alright, second lesson was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328640.0,
      "end_time": 333376.0,
      "text": "smell the roses. And the dirt. And the fertilizer."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 333400.0,
      "end_time": 336135.0,
      "text": "After Chung, I thanked this man."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 336160.0,
      "end_time": 338160.0,
      "text": "This is Ed Kaufmann."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338400.0,
      "end_time": 343576.0,
      "text": "And Ed is the one who chooses which coffee they serve at my local coffee shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 343600.0,
      "end_time": 347256.0,
      "text": "He goes around the world, to South America, to Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 347280.0,
      "end_time": 349950.0,
      "text": "finding the best coffee beans."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 349120.0,
      "end_time": 350536.0,
      "text": "So I thanked Ed."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 350560.0,
      "end_time": 356336.0,
      "text": "And in return, Ed showed me how to taste coffee like a pro."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 356360.0,
      "end_time": 358296.0,
      "text": "And it is quite a ritual."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 358320.0,
      "end_time": 360575.0,
      "text": "You take your spoon and you dip it in the coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360600.0,
      "end_time": 363376.0,
      "text": "and then you take a big, loud slurp."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 363400.0,
      "end_time": 365335.0,
      "text": "Almost cartoonishly loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 365360.0,
      "end_time": 368656.0,
      "text": "This is because you want to spray the coffee all over your mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 368680.0,
      "end_time": 371816.0,
      "text": "You have taste buds in the side of your cheeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 371840.0,
      "end_time": 373256.0,
      "text": "in the roof of your mouth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373280.0,
      "end_time": 374816.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got to get them all."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374840.0,
      "end_time": 377575.0,
      "text": "So Ed would do this"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 377600.0,
      "end_time": 380960.0,
      "text": "and he would --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 380120.0,
      "end_time": 382816.0,
      "text": "his face would light up and he would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 382840.0,
      "end_time": 386816.0,
      "text": "\"This coffee tastes of honey-crisp apple"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386840.0,
      "end_time": 390376.0,
      "text": "and notes of soil and maple syrup.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 390400.0,
      "end_time": 393150.0,
      "text": "And I would take a sip and I&#39;d say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 393400.0,
      "end_time": 395776.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m picking up coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 395800.0,
      "end_time": 397616.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 397640.0,
      "end_time": 399496.0,
      "text": "It tastes to me like coffee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 399520.0,
      "end_time": 401536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 401560.0,
      "end_time": 404496.0,
      "text": "But inspired by Ed, I decided to really"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 404520.0,
      "end_time": 407656.0,
      "text": "let the coffee sit on my tongue for five seconds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 407680.0,
      "end_time": 409896.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re all busy, but I could spare five seconds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409920.0,
      "end_time": 416456.0,
      "text": "and really think about the texture and the acidity and the sweetness."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 416480.0,
      "end_time": 418816.0,
      "text": "And I started to do it with other foods."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 418840.0,
      "end_time": 424496.0,
      "text": "And this idea of savoring is so important to gratitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 424520.0,
      "end_time": 427856.0,
      "text": "Psychologists talk about how gratitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 427880.0,
      "end_time": 433216.0,
      "text": "is about taking a moment and holding on to it as long as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 433240.0,
      "end_time": 436896.0,
      "text": "And slowing down time."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 436920.0,
      "end_time": 441696.0,
      "text": "So that life doesn&#39;t go by in one big blur, as it often does."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 441720.0,
      "end_time": 443176.0,
      "text": "Number three is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443200.0,
      "end_time": 446176.0,
      "text": "find the hidden masterpieces all around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 446200.0,
      "end_time": 449960.0,
      "text": "Now, one of my favorite conversations during this year"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 449120.0,
      "end_time": 453576.0,
      "text": "was with the guy who invented my coffee cup lid."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 453600.0,
      "end_time": 455256.0,
      "text": "And until this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455280.0,
      "end_time": 459455.0,
      "text": "I had given approximately zero thought to coffee cup lids."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459480.0,
      "end_time": 462736.0,
      "text": "But I loved talking to this inventor, Doug Fleming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 462760.0,
      "end_time": 464616.0,
      "text": "because he was so passionate."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464640.0,
      "end_time": 468616.0,
      "text": "And the blood and sweat and tears he put into this lid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 468640.0,
      "end_time": 471936.0,
      "text": "and that I had never even considered."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 471960.0,
      "end_time": 474816.0,
      "text": "He says a bad lid can ruin your coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 474840.0,
      "end_time": 476775.0,
      "text": "That it can block the aroma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 476800.0,
      "end_time": 479560.0,
      "text": "which is so important to the experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479800.0,
      "end_time": 481616.0,
      "text": "So he -- he&#39;s very innovative."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 481640.0,
      "end_time": 483695.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s like the Elon Musk of coffee lids."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 483720.0,
      "end_time": 484736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 484760.0,
      "end_time": 488976.0,
      "text": "So he designed this lid that&#39;s got an upside-down hexagon"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 489000.0,
      "end_time": 492976.0,
      "text": "so you can get your nose right in there and get maximum aroma."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 493000.0,
      "end_time": 496656.0,
      "text": "And so I was delighted talking to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 496680.0,
      "end_time": 501296.0,
      "text": "and it made me realize there are hundreds of masterpieces all around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 501320.0,
      "end_time": 503560.0,
      "text": "that we totally take for granted."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 503800.0,
      "end_time": 509536.0,
      "text": "Like the on-off switch on my desk lamp has a little indentation for my thumb"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 509560.0,
      "end_time": 511336.0,
      "text": "that perfectly fits my thumb."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 511360.0,
      "end_time": 514576.0,
      "text": "And when something is done well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 514600.0,
      "end_time": 517856.0,
      "text": "the process behind it is largely invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 517880.0,
      "end_time": 520960.0,
      "text": "But paying attention to it"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 520120.0,
      "end_time": 524336.0,
      "text": "can tap into that sense of wonder and enrich our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524360.0,
      "end_time": 527336.0,
      "text": "Number four is: fake it till you feel it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 527360.0,
      "end_time": 531296.0,
      "text": "By the end of the project, I was just in a thanking frenzy."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 531320.0,
      "end_time": 534496.0,
      "text": "So I was -- I would get up and spend a couple hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 534520.0,
      "end_time": 538376.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d write emails, send notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 538400.0,
      "end_time": 540935.0,
      "text": "make phone calls, visit people"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 540960.0,
      "end_time": 543136.0,
      "text": "to thank them for their role in my coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 543160.0,
      "end_time": 545415.0,
      "text": "And some of them, quite honestly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 545440.0,
      "end_time": 547296.0,
      "text": "not that into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 547320.0,
      "end_time": 549576.0,
      "text": "They would be like, \"What is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549600.0,
      "end_time": 553760.0,
      "text": "Is this a pyramid scheme, what do you want, what are you selling?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 554560.0,
      "end_time": 558815.0,
      "text": "But most people were surprisingly moved."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 558840.0,
      "end_time": 562616.0,
      "text": "I remember, I called the woman who does the pest control"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 562640.0,
      "end_time": 565816.0,
      "text": "for the warehouse where my coffee is served --"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 565840.0,
      "end_time": 568416.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sorry -- where my coffee is stored."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 568440.0,
      "end_time": 570896.0,
      "text": "And I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 570920.0,
      "end_time": 572415.0,
      "text": "\"This may sound strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 572440.0,
      "end_time": 576816.0,
      "text": "but I want to thank you for keeping the bugs out of my coffee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 576840.0,
      "end_time": 579456.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Well, that does sound strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 579480.0,
      "end_time": 581576.0,
      "text": "but you just made my day.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 581600.0,
      "end_time": 585176.0,
      "text": "And it was like an anti-crank phone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 585200.0,
      "end_time": 588576.0,
      "text": "And it didn&#39;t just affect her, it affected me."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 588600.0,
      "end_time": 594576.0,
      "text": "Because I would wake up every morning in my default mood, which is grumpiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 594600.0,
      "end_time": 597856.0,
      "text": "but I would force myself to write a thank-you note"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 597880.0,
      "end_time": 599976.0,
      "text": "and then another and then another."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 600000.0,
      "end_time": 604816.0,
      "text": "And what I found was that if you act as if you&#39;re grateful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 604840.0,
      "end_time": 607856.0,
      "text": "you eventually become grateful for real."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 607880.0,
      "end_time": 612776.0,
      "text": "The power of our actions to change our mind is astounding."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 612800.0,
      "end_time": 616856.0,
      "text": "So, often we think that thought changes behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 616880.0,
      "end_time": 621800.0,
      "text": "but behavior very often changes our thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 622720.0,
      "end_time": 627176.0,
      "text": "And finally, the last lesson I want to tell you about is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 627200.0,
      "end_time": 630616.0,
      "text": "practice six degrees of gratitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 630640.0,
      "end_time": 635216.0,
      "text": "And every place, every stop on this gratitude trail"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 635240.0,
      "end_time": 639136.0,
      "text": "would give birth to 100 other people that I could thank."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 639160.0,
      "end_time": 644415.0,
      "text": "So I went down to Colombia to thank the farmers who grow my coffee beans."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 644440.0,
      "end_time": 646656.0,
      "text": "And it was in a small mountain town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 646680.0,
      "end_time": 651856.0,
      "text": "and I was driven there along these curvy, cliffside roads."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 651880.0,
      "end_time": 655616.0,
      "text": "And every time we went around a hairpin turn"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 655640.0,
      "end_time": 659295.0,
      "text": "the driver would do the sign of the cross."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 659320.0,
      "end_time": 662176.0,
      "text": "And I was like, \"Thank you for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 662200.0,
      "end_time": 664160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 667856.0,
      "text": "But can you do that while keeping your hands on the wheel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 667880.0,
      "end_time": 669456.0,
      "text": "Because I am terrified.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 669480.0,
      "end_time": 670696.0,
      "text": "But we made it."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 670720.0,
      "end_time": 674216.0,
      "text": "And I met the farmers, the Guarnizo brothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 674240.0,
      "end_time": 677496.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a small farm, they make great coffee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 677520.0,
      "end_time": 680415.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re paid above fair-trade prices for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 680440.0,
      "end_time": 683456.0,
      "text": "And they showed me how the coffee is grown."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 683480.0,
      "end_time": 688560.0,
      "text": "The bean is actually inside this fruit called the coffee cherry."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 688800.0,
      "end_time": 690256.0,
      "text": "And I thanked them."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 690280.0,
      "end_time": 693496.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"Well, we couldn&#39;t do our job"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 693520.0,
      "end_time": 695736.0,
      "text": "without 100 other people.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 695760.0,
      "end_time": 699616.0,
      "text": "The machine that depulps the fruit is made in Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 699640.0,
      "end_time": 702696.0,
      "text": "and the pickup truck they drive around the farm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 702720.0,
      "end_time": 706136.0,
      "text": "that is made from parts from all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 706160.0,
      "end_time": 710256.0,
      "text": "In fact, the US exports steel to Colombia."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 710280.0,
      "end_time": 715256.0,
      "text": "So I went to Indiana, and I thanked the steel makers."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 715280.0,
      "end_time": 718415.0,
      "text": "And it just drove home"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 718440.0,
      "end_time": 722160.0,
      "text": "that it doesn&#39;t take a village to make a cup of coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 722400.0,
      "end_time": 725175.0,
      "text": "It takes the world to make a cup of coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 725200.0,
      "end_time": 730296.0,
      "text": "And this global economy, this globalization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 730320.0,
      "end_time": 732136.0,
      "text": "it does have downsides."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 732160.0,
      "end_time": 735616.0,
      "text": "But I believe the long-term upsides are far greater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 735640.0,
      "end_time": 737216.0,
      "text": "that progress is real."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 737240.0,
      "end_time": 739656.0,
      "text": "We have made improvements in the last 50 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 739680.0,
      "end_time": 742376.0,
      "text": "poverty worldwide has gone down."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 742400.0,
      "end_time": 745656.0,
      "text": "And that we should resist the temptation"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 745680.0,
      "end_time": 748695.0,
      "text": "to retreat into our silos."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 748720.0,
      "end_time": 751776.0,
      "text": "And we should resist this upsurge"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 751800.0,
      "end_time": 756335.0,
      "text": "in isolationism and jingoism."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 756360.0,
      "end_time": 758736.0,
      "text": "Which brings me to my final point."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 758760.0,
      "end_time": 764360.0,
      "text": "Which is my hope that we use gratitude as a spark to action."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 765360.0,
      "end_time": 769960.0,
      "text": "Some people worry that gratitude has a downside."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 769120.0,
      "end_time": 772936.0,
      "text": "That we&#39;ll be so grateful, that we&#39;ll be complacent."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 772960.0,
      "end_time": 776616.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll be so, \"Oh, everything&#39;s wonderful, I&#39;m so grateful.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 776640.0,
      "end_time": 780240.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out, the opposite is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 781120.0,
      "end_time": 783416.0,
      "text": "The research shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 783440.0,
      "end_time": 788960.0,
      "text": "that the more grateful you are, the more likely you are to help others."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 788120.0,
      "end_time": 790176.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re in a bad state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 790200.0,
      "end_time": 792776.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re often more focused on your own needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 792800.0,
      "end_time": 796160.0,
      "text": "But gratitude makes you want to pay it forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 796400.0,
      "end_time": 798456.0,
      "text": "And I experienced this personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 798480.0,
      "end_time": 800176.0,
      "text": "I mean, I&#39;m not Mother Teresa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 800200.0,
      "end_time": 803656.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m still a selfish bastard a huge amount of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 803680.0,
      "end_time": 807656.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m better than I was before this project."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 807680.0,
      "end_time": 810415.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because it made me aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 810440.0,
      "end_time": 814160.0,
      "text": "of the exploitation on the supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 814400.0,
      "end_time": 816976.0,
      "text": "It reminded me that what I take for granted"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 817000.0,
      "end_time": 820776.0,
      "text": "is not available to millions of people around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 820800.0,
      "end_time": 822550.0,
      "text": "Like water."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 822800.0,
      "end_time": 826376.0,
      "text": "Coffee is 98.8 percent water."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 826400.0,
      "end_time": 829935.0,
      "text": "So I figured I should go and thank the people at the New York reservoir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 829960.0,
      "end_time": 832576.0,
      "text": "hundreds of them, who provide me water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 832600.0,
      "end_time": 835696.0,
      "text": "and this miracle that I can turn a lever and get safe water."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 835720.0,
      "end_time": 839296.0,
      "text": "And that millions of people around the world don&#39;t have this luxury"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 839320.0,
      "end_time": 842296.0,
      "text": "and have to walk hours to get safe water."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 842320.0,
      "end_time": 847160.0,
      "text": "It inspired me to see what I could do to help people get more access,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 847400.0,
      "end_time": 850960.0,
      "text": "and I did research and found a wonderful group"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 850120.0,
      "end_time": 852776.0,
      "text": "called Dispensers for Safe Water."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 852800.0,
      "end_time": 854136.0,
      "text": "And I got involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 854160.0,
      "end_time": 856935.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m not expecting the Nobel Prize committee"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 856960.0,
      "end_time": 858216.0,
      "text": "to knock down my door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 858240.0,
      "end_time": 862536.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a baby step, it&#39;s a little something."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 862560.0,
      "end_time": 865376.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s all because of gratitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 865400.0,
      "end_time": 868935.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s why I encourage people, friends, family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 868960.0,
      "end_time": 871936.0,
      "text": "to follow gratitude trails of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 871960.0,
      "end_time": 874776.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s a life-transforming experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 874800.0,
      "end_time": 876415.0,
      "text": "And it doesn&#39;t have to be coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 876440.0,
      "end_time": 877656.0,
      "text": "It could be anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 877680.0,
      "end_time": 880215.0,
      "text": "It could be a pair of socks, it could be a light bulb."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 880240.0,
      "end_time": 883816.0,
      "text": "And you don&#39;t have to go around the world, you can just do a little gesture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 883840.0,
      "end_time": 888976.0,
      "text": "like make eye contact or send a note to the designer of a logo you love."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 889000.0,
      "end_time": 890976.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s more about a mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 891000.0,
      "end_time": 895480.0,
      "text": "Being aware of the thousands of people involved in every little thing we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 896880.0,
      "end_time": 899976.0,
      "text": "Remembering that there&#39;s someone in a factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 900000.0,
      "end_time": 904216.0,
      "text": "who made the fabric for the chairs you&#39;re sitting in right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 904240.0,
      "end_time": 910376.0,
      "text": "That someone went into a mine and got the copper for this microphone"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 910400.0,
      "end_time": 912976.0,
      "text": "so that I could say my final thank you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 913000.0,
      "end_time": 914856.0,
      "text": "which is to thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 914880.0,
      "end_time": 917760.0,
      "text": "Thank you a thousand for listening to my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 918400.0,
      "end_time": 920616.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 920640.0,
      "end_time": 922360.0,
      "text": "(Cheering)"
    }
  ]
}